Yekaterinburg

Yekaterinburg is a city in Sverdlovsk, in Russia.

GPS Coordinates of Yekaterinburg, Sverdlovsk, Russia

Yekaterinburg is located on the latitude of 56.8519 and longitude of 60.6122 and has a geohash of v6557m86qdk1.

Cities and Towns near Yekaterinburg

The nearest significant population center from Yekaterinburg is Shirokaya Rechka in Sverdlovsk, Russia, located 9 kilometers or 6 miles ↙ SW of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Shuvakish (Sverdlovsk, Russia) located 11 km (6 mi) ← W and Istok (Sverdlovsk, Russia) located 12 km (7 mi) → E of Yekaterinburg.

In total, we found 32 cities near Yekaterinburg in our database.
